  "title": "Event Admin Support (6–7 Months)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore Botanic Gardens | Gardens by the Bay (during show &amp; setup period)</p>\n<p><strong>Contract Duration:</strong> 6–7 months (Able to start from February 2026)</p>\n<p><strong>Number of Positions:</strong> 1</p>\n<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 8:30am – 6:00pm, Monday to Friday</p>\n<p><strong>Hourly Rate:</strong> $16.00 – $18.00 per hour</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br>\nWe are looking for an organized and proactive Event Administrative Support to assist our Festivals and Shows team. You will play a key role in supporting events leading up to and during the show period in July 2026. Your responsibilities will include:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Supporting the production of a new coffee table book, including organising photo libraries and coordinating with the publisher/writer.</li>\n  <li>Assisting in volunteer management, including coordination of tee shirts, Access Passes, Lanyards, and Volunteer Lounge arrangements.</li>\n  <li>Providing support for ceremonies, including catering coordination.</li>\n  <li>Coordinating VIP visits.</li>\n  <li>Assisting in organising and participating in roadshows and publicity efforts leading up to the event.</li>\n  <li>Undertaking other ad-hoc duties as required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree in relevant fields.</li>\n  <li>Strong organizational and coordination skills.</li>\n  <li>Proactive, detail-oriented, and able to work independently.</li>\n  <li>Experience in event administration or volunteer management is a plus.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No.: 96C4864 (Shanice Lim Xin Ni)</p>\n<p>Reg. No.: R22110485</p>\n<p><br></p>",
